CBRE Australian Healthcare & Social Infrastructure & Melbourne Office Leasing are pleased to offer for lease 165 Rosslyn Street, West Melbourne. A brand new premium healthcare opportunity in West End which is a bold new destination for Melbourne. Bounded by Rosslyn, Dudley and Adderley Streets it is an extension of the greater Melbourne CBD. Designed with active shopfronts, a public park and a creative laneway, workers, local residents and visitors will converge in its vibrant plaza, a destination for all.

+ A location with unparalleled connectivity, West Melbourne is one block from the city’s free tram zone and walking distance to train stations, parks, shops, restaurants and the buzzing CBD. The best of Melbourne is at your doorstep

+ A gateway address to the rest of Melbourne with Southern Cross Railway Station is within immediate proximity (600m*), offering train connections to the City Loop and the suburbs and the new North Melbourne Railway Station (soon to be renamed West Melbourne) is also within easy reach

+ An 80,000sqm* mixed use precinct made up of active shopfronts, a public park, supermarket, gym, day spa and creative laneway

+ Future ready with car share, electric vehicle charge stations, 103 bike racks, electric bike stations and end of trip facilities

Rarely does an opportunity exist to be located with premium referral partners located in your building, no more so that Nexus Hospital, Australia’s second largest day hospital platform with a national footprint of day and short-stay hospitals across six states and territories in Australia.

645-647 Burwood Highway, Vermont South offers:

+ Multiple tenancy options available ranging from 57sqm*- 290sqm* across three (3) levels

+ Significant parking for 206 cars across both basement and open-air spaces

+ Striking internal design features and an abundance of natural light in all tenancies
